When should we be ready?

474
00:25:33,157 --> 00:25:34,492
Uh...

475
00:25:34,492 --> 00:25:36,494
Oh, we‘re not
invited, Jack.

476
00:25:36,494 --> 00:25:37,828
Just her.

477
00:25:37,828 --> 00:25:38,954
Figures.

478
00:25:38,954 --> 00:25:40,331
That doesn‘t
seem fair.

479
00:25:40,331 --> 00:25:42,958
