Sorry to keep
you waiting.

483
00:26:07,400 --> 00:26:08,942
Come on out.

484
00:26:08,942 --> 00:26:10,277
Come on.

485
00:26:13,072 --> 00:26:16,283
Am I good,
or am I good?

486
00:26:22,248 --> 00:26:24,208
Look at all the people.

487
00:26:30,797 --> 00:26:32,508
Here they are.

488
00:26:33,842 --> 00:26:35,428
I don‘t remember
her being so...

489
00:26:35,428 --> 00:26:37,595
Beautiful.
Yeah.

490
00:26:37,595 --> 00:26:39,597
Everyone,
this is Sarina.

491
00:26:39,597 --> 00:26:40,807
Sarina,
this is everyone.

492
00:26:40,807 --> 00:26:42,600
Odo.
Nerys.

